why we go for deployment:
1-Real-world explanation

If your application gets updated from v1 to v2:

ğŸ‘‰ ReplicaSet cannot update version
ğŸ‘‰ Deployment updates pods without downtime, creates a new ReplicaSet internally, and rolls back if something breaks
ReplicaSet ensures the required number of Pods are running, while Deployment sits on top of ReplicaSet and adds rolling updates, rollbacks, and release strategies.
